    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean, u said it was a tactical victory but a strategic failure... but doesnt the fact that the country basically fell apart into chaos and became a vacuum for terrorism make the whole thing a failure from the start? like, if the end result is just more instability in north africa, how can anyone call it a success at all?",
